Start
   |
[Ask user for number of bottles]
   |
[Pass input to countdown function]
   |
V
-------------------------------------
|   Is number > 1?                  |
|      Yes --> [Print "X bottles"]  |
|                number -= 1        |
|                Loop back          |
|      No  --> [Print "1 bottle"]   |
|                number -= 1        |
|                Loop back if > 0   |
-------------------------------------
   |
[Print "Go buy more beer!"]
   |
End
